On the Republican side, the battle lines have mostly been drawn around who =
did, and did not, support Kevin McCarthy when he was ousted from the speake=
rship. On the Democratic side, the dividing line is all about Israel. This =
rundown is based on television ad spending, candidate fundraising, outside =
group spending, and of course, plenty of inside chatter.

* McCarthy=E2=80=99s vendetta: McCarthy is out for blood. The super PAC run=
